The paper discusses software maintenance activities and proposes visualizations to explore them. This topic falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The use of visualizations suggests a focus on human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. The use of the Shiny R framework suggests a focus on cybernetics (cs.CY) and systems and control (cs.SI) sub-categories.
